com.misc.common.moplaf.time.continuous

Interface DistributionEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, com.misc.common.moplaf.propagator.ObjectWithPropagatorFunctionAdapter
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AmountAbsolute, AmountAbsoluteAtomic, AmountImpulsion, AmountImpulsionAtomic, CapacityChangeEnd, CapacityChangeStart, ChildEvent, EndEvent, SlopeAbsolute, SlopeAbsoluteAtomic, SlopeImpulsion, SlopeImpulsionAtomic, StartEvent, StockChangeEnd, StockChangeStart
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmountAbsoluteAtomicImpl, AmountAbsoluteImpl, AmountImpulsionAtomicImpl, AmountImpulsionImpl, CapacityChangeEndImpl, CapacityChangeStartImpl, ChildEventImpl, DistributionEventImpl, EndEventImpl, SlopeAbsoluteAtomicImpl, SlopeAbsoluteImpl, SlopeImpulsionAtomicImpl, SlopeImpulsionImpl, StartEventImpl, StockChangeEndImpl, StockChangeStartImpl

    public interface DistributionEvent
extends com.misc.common.moplaf.propagator.ObjectWithPropagatorFunctionAdapter
    A representation of the model object 'Distribution Event'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Moment
    • Event Nr
    • Next
    • Previous
    • Amount Before
    • Amount After
    • Slope Before
    • Slope After
    • Description
    • Distribution As Sequence
    • Distribution As Provided Event
    See Also:
    ContinuousPackage.getDistributionEvent()
